name: DG TS Srl
about:
DG TS, precedentemente conosciuta come Officina De Giambattista, è uno dei maggiori produttori europei di montanti e componenti per Veicoli Industriali (principalmente per autotreni e furgoni). 
Profondo know-how, tecnologie moderne ed una forza lavoro altamente qualificata garantiscono una produzione altamente affidabile e di qualità, che ha portato DG TS ad essere un punto di riferimento nel mercato.
L'azienda vanta un'esperienza cinquantennale nel settore e conserva, ancora immutata, la voglia di innovare e di affrontare le sfide con entusiasmo e con la filosofia di progettare e produrre unicamente nei propri stabilimenti italiani (di DG TS e Twinex).

DG TS, formerly known as Officina De Giambattista since the '70, is one of the largest European manufacturers of pillars and components for trucks and trailers. 
High levels of know-how, modern technology and a highly qualified workforce guarantee the highly reliable and quality production which has led DG TS to be a benchmark within its market.
The company, with more than fifty years of experience in the sector, is still keeping the wish to innovate and facing the new challenges with passion and the philosophy of designing and manufacturing exclusively in the owned Italian facilities (DG TS and #Twinex).

about:
About Us:
Founded in 2022, Brown Bridges is a  student success consulting and technical assistance agency that assists with the strategic design, program implementation, and capacity-building for student success initiatives across all levels of higher education. Our work is deeply rooted in reconstructing and advancing systems, policies, and procedures to fundamentally improve student success outcomes for low-income students and students of color. We offer many services dedicated to student success operations, transfer/transition initiatives, and education technology/data integration.

Mission:
Brown Bridges partners with all levels of higher education organizations to ACCELERATE student success strategies focused on closing equity gaps and improving graduation outcomes for underserved students of color.

Vision:
Brown Bridges will assist in the reconstruction of higher education's student success operations and procedures to put marginalized students AT THE CENTER.

name: Duurzame Inzetbaarheid Katalysator
about:
Rollen en functies veranderen inhoudelijk als gevolg van veranderende strategie of koers van uw organisatie, nieuwe technologieën, digitalisering en automatisering,  uw moet uw medewerkers vragen langer door te werken, uw voorziet een reorganisatie of……
Allemaal redenen om eens te kijken hoe het staat met de duurzame inzetbaarheid van uw mensen binnen uw organisatie!

Duurzame inzetbaarheid van medewerkers behelst naast een goede gezondheid en het bijhouden van vakkennis,  persoonlijke ontwikkeling en groei, waarbij je uitgaat van de kwaliteiten/vaardigheden, wensen medewerker en doelstellingen van organisatie en gebruikt maakt van mogelijkheden die voor werknemer, team en organisatie positief zijn.

Wij geloven ….
 - Dat organisaties die werk maken van duurzame inzetbaarheid toekomstbestendig zijn.
 - Dat medewerkers het succes van de organisatie bepalen.
 - Dat duurzame inzetbaarheid een onderdeel is van integraal leiderschap
-  Dat duurzame inzetbaarheid maatwerk is, uniek voor iedere organisatie, uniek voor iedere medewerker
-   Dat een continue dialoog (over duurzame inzetbaarheid) tussen leidinggevenden en medewerkers essentieel is

De Duurzame Inzetbaarheid Katalysator kan u hierin adviseren door gezamenlijk een plan van aanpak te maken op organisatieniveau. 
- Wat is de aanleiding en wat is de ambitie, wat zijn de knelpunten?
- Wat is er al gedaan, wat werkt wel en wat niet?
- Inventarisatie bestaande instrumenten, tools en interventies
- Inzet diverse tools zoals:
     - Kosten-baten analyse KOBA-DI tool, ontwikkeld door TNO en NPDI
     - Bedrijfsscan
     - Werkenergieanalyse®
- Campagne voor bewustwording
Het resultaat is een gezamenlijk plan van aanpak op organisatieniveau.

 I moved towards my own educational goals and public service. I currently serve as a school board member and legislative representative (GRN) for Ogallala Public Schools. In addition to the aforementioned, I discovered my passion for education after traveling around the world and visiting schools in many countries. Moreover, I have had the opportunity to visit schools across the United States as well as across Nebraska through the Nebraska LEAD program.  



As a student of economics I understand the relationship between education and economic well- being. name: Marco Schreier Mineralienhandlung GmbH
about:
Seit 1981 ist dieser Mineralien-Großhandel in Ludwigsburg bei Stuttgart Ihr innovativer und zuverlässiger Partner für den Edelstein-, Heilsteine- und Schmuck-Fachhandel weltweit, sowie für Heilpraktiker, Therapeuten, Massagepraxen, Feng Shui Berater und andere Menschen, die in ihrem Beruf mit Mineralien und Edelsteinen arbeiten.

Mineralien und Edelsteine finden Anwendung in vielfältigster Form: im Schmuck, als werthaltige Geschenkartikel, als Heilsteine, in der Massage und Wellness und als Raum-Accessoires, Dekoration und Sammlungstücke.

In unserer Verkaufs-Ausstellung in Ludwigsburg (zwischen Stuttgart und Heilbronn) finden Sie auf über 1000m² alles rund um die Welt der Edelsteine von den Achat-Scheiben bis zum Zoisit-Trommelstein, z.B. Edelstein-Stränge, Verschlüsse und Zwischenteile aus Silber 925 und vergoldet, gebohrte Trommelsteine und andere Steinteile, Steine für die Edelstein-Massage und andere steinheilkundlichen Anwendungen, Design-Schmuck, Silberketten, Rohsteine und Kristalle. Die Ausstellung unseres Mineralien-Großhandels hat von Montag bis Freitag für Sie geöffnet. 

Schulungen und Seminare runden Ihr Programm für den Fachhandel ab.

Aufgeteilt nach den vier Qualitätsmarken Maulwurf - Geschenke aus der Natur®, Chili Creative®, Chili Jewels® sowie Lapis Vitalis® finden Sie ca. 10.000 Artikel im Onlineshop.

 "Qualität ist, wenn der Kunde zurück kommt, nicht das Produkt ...". Dieser Ausspruch gibt kurz und prägnant unser Selbstverständnis wieder. Wir wollen, dass Sie von unserer Auswahl und unserem Service begeistert sind und wir langfristig Ihr Vertrauen gewinnen. 

Unsere vielen Kontakte in alle Welt, die sich in über 30 Jahren unserer Firmengeschichte aufgebaut haben, nutzen wir dazu, ständig nach neuen Produkten und Artikeln für Sie zu suchen. Neben neuen Fundorten sind vor allem modisch top-aktuelle und saisonale Artikel interessant. 

Auf allen wichtigen Fachmessen sind wir mit einem Stand vertreten.

We partner with you to deliver consistent, reliable, safe, and proactive solutions that get what you need where you need it to go. 

As a strategic logistics partner, we’ll think forward to how to continuously improve your rate of successful deliveries and your customer satisfaction while managing your costs in the most responsible way. You’ve done the hard part: you have made the sales. Now, you need a logistics partner that will make you look your best at the finish line.

name: Smooth Sales
about:
Smooth Sales is a collective of sales experts. We help sales organisations win. 

We work on 3-24 month contracts with clients undergoing change delivering Sales Enablement or Sales Transformation projects, typically for PE or investor owned businesses. With deep experience in identifying issues and finding engaging solutions, Smooth Sales can change your sales culture and drive performance at scale. 

Smooth Sales started in 2017 and was built on 25 years of sales experience in Telecoms, Software & Data. Previous engagements include multiple contracts in Software & data businesses along with senior enablement roles in Fortune 500 businesses. We consistently deliver outstanding results in Sales Enablement & Sales Transformation projects across different industries. 

Ideally located with easy access to London, Heathrow & Gatwick with a proven ability to quickly get up to speed for outcome based contracts from 3-24 months. 

Typical clients are Private Equity invested businesses, recent acquisitions or businesses undergoing strategic change.

Specialities -

Sales Enablement – Track record of delivering award winning programs focusing on sales skills & sales knowledge
 
Sales Transformation – Sales health checks (benchmarking) Sales process optimisation, defining & delivering the right structure to execute on strategy.
 
Talent assessments - How good is your team, who are the stars, where do you need to invest or recruit?

Change programs – New CRM (2 x Global Salesforce roll outs), refreshing sales culture & skills, delivering new go to market approaches & training.
 
Interim Sales leadership - stepping in when a gap opens up.

Future leader coaching and mentoring - Investing in your team, empathetic & trustworthy 
 
Bespoke training - Opportunity generation, Account Planning, Strategic negotiation, Closing plans, Presentation skills
 
Speaking & Presenting – Coaching senior leaders 1-1 to turn a weakness into a strength

of delivering bulk logistic management to companies throughout North America.

As a leader in the industry, Premier Bulk Logistics only hires specific carriers that meet our 
rigorous standards.
 
Premier Bulk Logistics is small enough to deliver personal attention to all your transportation 
needs. We are available 24/7/365, no navigating through difficult phone menus, your call 
will be answered by one of our sales professionals.
 
At the same time Premier Bulk logistics is large enough to handle all your transportation 
needs. We have the ability to customize our service to meet your needs. 

We offer full service, establish pick up and delivery times, follow up with all loads to assure 
timely pick up and delivery times, and keep the customer informed at every point along the 
way.
 
So whether it is a move across the street or a move across the country, Premier Bulk 
Logistics is there to help.
 
So please, Let Us Take a Load Off Your Mind

Changing Horizons plug short term resource gaps within credit unions by providing operational resource services. We work remotely and operate within the credit unions own policy & procedures for functions such as loans underwriting, credit control and membership services. 

In our experience its usually left to the General Managers or CEO's to cover core functions at times when you are experiencing high seasonal volumes, staff holidays or sickness. Changing Horizons will step in and work with you and your team, and in doing so will give you back your time to focus growing the business and doing your own job instead of back filling for others.

name: Reykjafell
about:
Reykjafell was established in 1956 with a commitment to supplying electrical professionals in Iceland with quality products. 68 years later, the company continues to uphold this principle and provide a broad selection of quality electrical products to its customers. Reykjafell is a leading provider in the electrical industry.

Reykjafell's headquarters and distribution hub are based in the capital city of Reykjavik. Additionally, the company operates a regional branch in Akureyri in the northern part of Iceland, ensuring coverage across the country.

At Reykjafell, we're proud to offer our professional customers the convenience of our 24/7 web-shop. As an online store, we provide an easy and efficient way for our customers to order online, fast and easily, whether companies need delivered straight to their door, or prefer to pick up their products at our warehouse. With full control of their projects and quotes, all in one place, we make it simple for professionals. With Reykjafell's web-shop, you'll save time and streamline your operations. 

At Reykjafell, our focus is solely on the electrical sector. As a B2B provider, our goal is to offer exceptional service to our customers. We believe in delivering fast and secure solutions, tailored to the unique needs of electrical professionals. Our team of experts understand the demands of the industry, and we are committed to providing only the best products to meet those demands. Reykjafell is here to provide the highest-quality products and service for the electrical industry, by professionals for professionals. 

For six consecutive years, Reykjafell has been among the 2% of Icelandic companies that have met the requirements set by Creditinfo for being The Strongest in Iceland. Reykjafell also celebrates being recognized as Firm of the Year by VR, Store and Office Workers’ Union for the third time.

name: HDry
about:
HDry is the most advanced technology for waterproofing outdoor products through direct (3D) lamination of a waterproof/breathable membrane.
HDry enhances the technological development that its founders initiated in 2006 when they created the OutDry technology and associated brand. They were the very first to introduce the direct, three-dimensional, lamination process of a membrane onto an outdoor shoe upper, thereby winning the prestigious ISPO 'ECO DESIGN' AWARD in 2008. 

The ‘HDry’ brand derives from the abbreviation of the chemical name for water (H2O), coupled with the word ‘Dry’, and signifies the affinity between this technology and water. In fact, HDry technology interacts with water in multiple ways, at times acting as a protective element (from rain, snow or ice), at times as a conduit (allowing sweat to vaporize), all the while sustaining water from an environmental point of view.

name: Digital Competence Center M-Industry
about:
NETA - das Digital Competence Center der MIGROS Industrie und wurde als Teil der Schweizer MIGROS Gruppe gegründet, um 

• die strategische digitale Weiterentwicklung der M-Industrie voranzutreiben,
• die Digitale Transformation der 25 M-Industrie-Unternehmen aktiv zu pushen und
• Business Innovation für die gesamte MIGROS Gruppe zu initiieren und zu begleiten.

NETA betreibt die digitale Weiterentwicklung der MIGROS Industrie und der MIGROS Gruppe. Mit aktuellsten Innovations- und Design Methoden, agilem Mindset, hohem Qualitäts- und Leistungsanspruch und viel Start-up-Spirit. An den Standorten Birsfelden, Suhr und Berlin konzipiert, entwickelt, launched und betreibt ein junges, hochmotiviertes Team mit Experten und Talenten aus den Bereichen

• Consulting und Strategie
• Design und Text
• Concept und UX
• Product Management
• eCommerce
• IT-Development und Technology

schon heute wettbewerbsfähige digitale Produkte und Plattformen, erfolgreiche eBusinesses, Kampagnen, neue Geschäftsmodelle und Brands gemeinsam mit den MIGROS Industrie-Partnern. 

Die MIGROS ­Industrie gehört mit ihren 25 leistungsstarken Unternehmen in der Schweiz und den acht Betrieben im Ausland zur Schweizer MIGROS ­Gruppe. Mit einem Angebot von über 400 Marken und 20'000 hochwertigen Produkten in rund 50 Ländern ist die MIGROS Industrie einer der grössten Eigenmarkenproduzenten weltweit.

NETA. Für die digitale Weiterentwicklung der MIGROS Industrie und der MIGROS Gruppe.

about:
A Totus Corretora oferece soluções ágeis e simplificadas em seguros corporativos, atuando como parceira estratégica na gestão de riscos. Especializada em Seguros Garantia, Riscos de Engenharia e Responsabilidade Civil, protege obras, contratos e licitações em todo o Brasil. Com 11 anos de experiência, a Totus Corretora já atendeu mais de 800 clientes, acumulando R$2 bilhões em importância segurada e construindo um portfólio diversificado que abrange desde pequenas empresas até grandes corporações. A corretora opera em parceria com as principais seguradoras do mercado, garantindo soluções robustas e confiáveis.

Nosso diferencial reside no atendimento consultivo e personalizado. Nossa equipe é composta por especialistas altamente qualificados, que oferecem suporte técnico e estratégico para auxiliar os clientes na tomada de decisões. Além disso, a Totus Corretora oferece treinamentos e workshops para capacitar os clientes a entenderem melhor seus riscos e a utilizarem o seguro como ferramenta de proteção e crescimento. Focamos em transformar a gestão de riscos em vantagem competitiva, oferecendo coberturas personalizadas e expertise técnica em cada etapa do processo.

name: EkşioğluLife
about: EKŞİOĞLU LIFE 1970 yılında İmdat EKŞİ ve Mustafa EKŞİ kardeşler tarafından kurulan bir aile şirketidir. 40 yılı aşkın süredir faaliyetlerine Kadıköy ve Üsküdar bölgelerinde devam etmekte olup, sektördeki engin tecrübe ve birikimi ile yüzlerce daireyi sahiplerine teslim etmiştir. İsmi sektörde “Güven” algısı ile anılan EKŞİOĞLU LIFE “Doğru zamanda doğru proje” anlayışı ile faaliyetlerini sürdürmektedir. Güven algısını oluşturan en temel noktalar ülkemizin red edilemez bir gerçeği olan doğal afetlere karşı maksimum dayanıklılığı sağlayan yapılar oluşturmak ve vaat edilmiş teslim tarihlerine uymaktır. Kendini her gün geliştiren ve bu gelişim sonucunda da değiştiren EKŞİOĞLU LIFE projelerini mimari açıdan insana huzur ve keyif veren çalışmalar olarak gerçekleştirirken yatırım değeri yüksek ve yükselmekte olan işlere de imza atmıştır. Müşteri odaklı yapısı sayesinde “Müşteri Memnuniyeti” konusunda çok iddalı bir kurumdur. Faaliyet göstermeye başladığı zamandan beri teknolojik gelişmeleri takip ederek her zaman en modern projelerin mimarı olmuştur. Projelerini üretirken şehrin yeşil alan ihtiyaçlarını da göz önünde bulunduran bir anlayış ile barınma merkezinden çok “Yaşam Alanı” anlayışını benimsemiştir. Firma çalışmaları ikinci kuşak Ahmet Sami EKŞİ başkanlığında devam etmektedir.

name: Hebron Rehabilitation Committee
about:
The Hebron Rehabilitation Committee (HRC) is a semi-governmental organisation dedicated to the revitalisation of the Old City of Hebron. The HRC offices are located within the Old City, in an area which is currently under Israeli military control.
HRC was established as a semi-governmental organisation in 1996 by a presidential declaration from former Palestinian leader Yasser Arafat in order to rehabilitate the Old City of Hebron.
HRC aims at i. rehabilitating and restoring historical buildings in Hebron Old City, as well as ii. to preserve these ancient historical buildings, iii. ensure economic and social revival, iv. maintain ties between the Old City and Hebron in general, v. encourage inhabitants to return to the Old City and vi. improve living conditions for marginalized groups by planning and executing vital projects to ensure economic, social and cultural revival.
HRC's housing programme’s key objectives include the re-population of the deteriorated city centre, the preservation of cultural heritage, local economic development, the engagement of the population and the provision of affordable housing.
The main components of the programme include the securing of decent housing, infrastructure and services, the stimulation of economic activity, and the provision of legal assistance to protect the residents' rights. As a result of the programme, several thousand new residents have moved into the Old City. Economic conditions are improving and the social fabric of the area has been strengthened by social integration awareness and community participation.

name: Hochschule 21
about:
Die hochschule 21 entwickelt interdisziplinäre, berufsbegleitende Angebote zur Fort- und Weiterbildung. Träger der Veranstaltungen sind sowohl die hochschuleigenen Anbieter von Fort- und Weiterbildung als auch Kooperations- und Netzwerkpartner.
Das Akronym IWB steht für „Institut für Weiterbildung und Bauprüfung - Institut an der Hochschule 21 zur Förderung des Technologietransfers in der Elbe-Weser-Region e.V.“ Das IWB ist seit 2007 als eigenständiger Verein erfolgreich aktiv und in der Hochschule verortet. Insbesondere werden Fortbildungen aus dem Bereich Bauwesen angeboten, die aktuelle Themen und neue Anforderungen an das Bauwesen aufgreifen und somit einen wesentlichen Bestandteil der Fort- und Weiterbildung an der hochschule 21 darstellt.
Das IWB bietet Fortbildungsseminare für Berufstätige, i. d. R. abends mit vier Unterrichtseinheiten zu unterschiedlichen aktuellen Themenfelder der Baubranche an. Die angebotenen Seminare werden durch die Ingenieurkammer Niedersachsen zur Dokumentation der Fortbildungsverpflichtung anerkannt. Außerdem bietet das IWB dena-anerkannte Weiterbildungslehrgänge für Energieeffizienz-Expert*innen (EEE) (in Kooperation des IWB mit der Handwerkskammer Hamburg im Elbcampus in Hamburg-Harburg).
Sprechen Sie uns gerne jederzeit an oder kontaktieren uns via E-Mail: iwb@hs21.de.
Weitere Informationen zum IWB und zu unserem aktuellen Programm, das stetig aktualisiert wird, erhalten Sie unter www.hs21.de/iwb.

name: INVESTINSPAIN
about:
INVESTINSPAIN is an International real estate agency on the Costa Del Sol, with offices in Spain and Belgium, thereby assisting people - looking to enjoy life or invest - with the purchase of a property in the sunny South. 
More and more people from all parts of Europe (and beyond) are looking for a property in the Costa Del Sol for the following reasons;

- Low interest rates (= time to borrow, and especially not to save!)
- Growing Spanish real estate market
- Very strict new building standards in Spain & nice architecture
- Excellent rentability on a seasonal basis (min. 5% on an annual basis)
- Easy accessibility by plane from all airports in Europe
- Low living costs 
- Warmest climate in Europe 
- Culinary enjoyment of high-quality Mediterranean cuisine
- Last but not least... You increase your quality of life (a piece of paradise at a few hours by plane)

Buying a property abroad, however, is different from buying at home. An estate agent who knows the region through and through and speaks your language is of primary importance! 
We are therefore happy to assist our clients with the following services, among others; 
- Completion of local mandatory formalities (application N.I.E. number, opening bank account, appointing notary &  lawyer)
- Translation of all documentation from Spanish to your language
- Connection of utilities
- Security (alarm & camera surveillance)
- Wifi & network installations
- Furnishing of your property (choose from our BE showroom or ES show flat, and we deliver in your premises)
- Property management (garden maintenance, cleaning services, key-holding, ...)

name: Correduría De Seguros García Ochoa - Gestores De Seguros
about:
En Correduría de Seguros García-Ochoa somos una correduría de seguros independiente y llevamos más de 30 años en el mercado velando por la mejor opción para nuestros clientes. Estamos especializados en seguros para empresas y particulares. Contamos con el respaldo de las compañías aseguradoras más solventes.

Con nosotros tienes a especialistas en todos los entresijos de los seguros que velan directamente por tu bienestar.

En Seguros García-Ochoa analizamos tu situación empresarial, personal, familiar y patrimonial e identificamos tus necesidades concretas para que en caso de necesitar usar tus pólizas estés realmente protegido.

Un seguro lo puedes contratar por teléfono, incluso online. Pero lo que realmente debes saber con seguridad es que tienes las coberturas que realmente necesitas, que pagas el mejor precio y que ante cualquier siniestro o situación que necesites de tu seguro, nosotros estaremos ahí para que todas las coberturas se cumplan de forma rápida y satisfactoria. Resolvemos tus siniestros rápidamente.

Disponemos de seguros para empresa y familias. Si quieres trabajar con especialistas que solucionen tus necesidades danos unos minutos de tu tiempo y te explicaremos personalmente nuestra forma de trabajar.
Contamos con un equipo de profesionales de 10 personas velando por los intereses de nuestros clientes, muchos de ellos desde hace más de 10 años en nuestra correduría. Ellos son nuestro mayor capital y te atenderán diligentemente para que siempre estés bien protegido.

En la actualidad, en Correduría de Seguros García-Ochoa contamos con más de 4.000 clientes entre particulares, autónomos y empresas, y realizamos todo tipo de seguros. Ofrecemos nuestros servicios de seguros en todo el territorio español, siendo de las provincias de Castilla-La Mancha y de la Comunidad de Madrid donde contamos con más clientes.

name: Global Emergency Response and Assistance (GERA)
about:
The mission of Global Emergency Response and Assistance is to protect human rights, and restore the dignity, well-being, and safety of those physically, emotionally, and mentally affected by conflicts. We provide aid and assistance to refugees, new arrivals in host countries, and internally displaced persons. By assisting such individuals with basic supplies and supporting their assimilation processes both physically and psychologically, we help support the values of human dignity and human rights.

VISION

GERA’s vision is to help create, advocate for, and manifest a world in which every refugee, migrant, or displaced person receives the basic living necessities to ensure that they live a healthy and just life in accordance with the Universal Declaration of Human Rights. GERA is a grassroots NGO directly engaging with and assisting the populations we are to serve, as laid out in our mission; whether that be in the United States of America or elsewhere around the world.

We envision ourselves as a grassroots NGO helping people survive directly on the front lines in conflict situations, similar to the way Peter did through SERA. At GERA we believe that saving the life of one person is a step towards saving all of humanity.

about:
S&S Fabricators was founded in 2003 by two master carpenters looking to become independent business owners. What started then as custom renovation work has today grown into S&S Mechanical, a comprehensive mechanical services firm serving in Maryland, DC, Virginia, North Carolina, and Delaware.

We have 6 service divisions:

     • Refrigeration
     • HVAC
     • Kitchen Equipment
     • Electrical
     • Plumbing
     • General Maintenance

We take pride in hiring not only good technicians but the best technicians. We then empower them to meet and exceed our customers' expectations on every job.

We're in business to provide our customers with worry-free mechanical services and maintenance. We want to make sure that our customers never have to be concerned with the safe, effective, and efficient function of their mechanical equipment - we'll take care of it.

We are committed to being responsive, passionate, and knowledgeable. Every member of our team is equally dedicated to both the work they do and the customers they serve.

We never rest on our laurels. We have continuing education and innovation programs built into our long-term plans to ensure that we're always providing our customers with the most effective service and recommendations.

For us, it all boils down to service. From management to technicians to office staff, we take pride in always being responsive to and respectful of our customers' needs.

name: Greenway Demolition Pty Ltd
about:
Greenway Demolition provides professional demolition services in South East Queensland. Whether your project is to knock-down and rebuild, demolish redundant amenities or buildings, asbestos removal, or building strip-outs, you’ll experience a completely transparent and professional approach to demolition.

Greenway Demolition’s Director Amery Kim, began working in the demolition industry in 2006. Amery began surgically removing buildings and offices in inner Sydney, where planning and preparation was key. Amery relocated to the Gold Coast in 2019 and Greenway Demolition was formed.

Greenway Demolition’s focus is based on quality and environmentally sound practices, and the Greenway Demolition team prides itself on being:

Safe
Organised
Professional
On-time
Efficient
Skilled

A local family owned and operated SME business, Greenway Demolition takes pride in providing a service delivered to its clients by a skilled team of professionals who manage customer projects from start to finish.

Drawing on over 120 years of combined experience in the industry, Greenway Demolition team members are trusted by builders, developers, and homeowners as a safe, reliable solution provider. Greenway Demolition uses specialised equipment to ensure each structure is systematically demolished using tried and tested processes that are efficient and cost-effective.

On top of securing permits and approvals, Greenway Demolition also conducts the correct site preparation and after-project clean-up to ensure delivery is a smooth and streamlined service from inception to completion.

Greenway Demolition undertakes complete or partial demolitions and with its well-managed, cost-effective service, often works on occupied premises, with consideration for those working around them, allowing routines to progress as usual.

Osnovna djelatnost Zavoda za izgradnju je istraživanje, organizovanje i posredovanje u izgradnji stambenih, javnih i drugih objekata, te upravljanje stambenim, garažnim i poslovnim prostorima na teritoriji grada Banja Luka.

U okviru svoje djelatnosti Zavod obavlja:
- stručne poslove u vezi izgradnje i održavanja stambenih i poslovnih objekata, objekata infrastrukture i uređenja građevinskog zemljišta (inženjering),

- knjigovodstvene, finansijske, pravne, istraživačko-razvojne i sve druge poslove u vezi upravljanja udruženim stambenim fondom.

name: RNW Media
about:
RNW Media is an international media development organisation based in Haarlem, the Netherlands, dedicated to harness the power of independent digital media to uphold human rights and advance the public good.

Working in more than 40 countries across Europe, North Africa, the Middle East, West and East Africa, East Asia, Central and South America, we defend media and internet freedom, the right of every human being to access to information and freedom of expression.

With over 75 years of experience, RNW Media has evolved from an international radio broadcaster into a champion of independent digital media. Our work with our partners has demonstrated how a diverse, resilient, and trustworthy digital media ecosystem can inform people, shift narratives, influence social norms, and drive policy change, reinforcing the essential role of independent media in open and democratic societies.

RNTC, the internationally renowned training centre of RNW Media, provides journalism and media training to journalists, media makers and communication professionals.

Through The Vine, RNW Media’s global community, with more than 25 independent and public interest digital media, 80 media trainers, and 10,000 RNTC alumni, we facilitate media coalition, partnership and movement building.

name: Early Me
about:
Your journey is unique, but many of your memories are lodged deep in the archives of your mind. There are a few you readily break out and share when the family comes over, but there are so many you haven’t dusted off in a long time.

Your family and friends will help you dig up all those beloved memories. As they ask you questions you’ll remember experiences, feelings, and emotions you’ve long forgotten. As you share your memories and respond to follow-up questions, you’ll rediscover your past.

You are probably on other social media platforms, as you should be. But this is different. Many other platforms help you share what you’re doing now or a couple days ago. Sometimes you may even reminisce.

But Early Me is designed to help you dive into your past and build a timeline that your family and friends can use to really get to know you.
